    "text": "$$\n\\text{Số trung bình: } \\bar{x} = \\frac{8 \\cdot 6,75 + 10 \\cdot 7,25 + \\cdots + 4 \\cdot 9,75}{82} = \\frac{666}{82} \\approx 8,122.\n$$"
